  "1783560": {
    "name": "The Last Caretaker",
    "steam_appid": 1783560,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是最后的守护者，一台被重新激活的机器人，肩负拯救人类未来的重任。你将在被海洋淹没的广袤世界中探索，利用手头有限的资源在深度十足的制作系统中进行制作，从而开辟通向目标的道路，打造拯救人类的工具。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地球已被海洋吞没，浩瀚苍穹之下，各种旧世界的巍峨巨构正逐渐锈蚀。《The Last Caretaker》中，你要做的不仅是生存，更需要进行探索。你的选择将塑造故事的走向，开启一段引人深思的，从海洋延伸至群星的个性化冒险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《The Last Caretaker》对生存制作类型进行了深度诠释，在游戏中，你所做的每个决定、执行的每个行动，都会有其相应的后果。沉浸于这个精心打造的世界，在这里，人类的命运就握在你的手中。你的任务已然明确：找回人类的种子，重启Lazarus Complex，将人类最后的希望送入星辰大海。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783560/extras/3ce33ea5a0a5d3e77dd474daa9801c6b.poster.avif?t=1770805760\" width=780 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783560/extras/3ce33ea5a0a5d3e77dd474daa9801c6b.webm?t=1770805760\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783560/extras/3ce33ea5a0a5d3e77dd474daa9801c6b.mp4?t=1770805760\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >培育人类</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在Lazarus Complex中培育并照料人类的种子，管理培育温度、营养调配与记忆数据整合等关键系统。解锁高级生物仓以及合成人看护者，加速发展进度，确保成功复活。探索每颗种子内封存的情感印记与过往的记忆，在让世界重焕生机的同时，拼凑出那已经失落在时间长河之中的人类故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783560/extras/0c61710ca690e57114dffd4779e9b87a.poster.avif?t=1770805760\" width=780 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783560/extras/0c61710ca690e57114dffd4779e9b87a.webm?t=1770805760\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783560/extras/0c61710ca690e57114dffd4779e9b87a.mp4?t=1770805760\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >保护人类</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从叛变的机械和环境的威胁手下保卫Lazarus Complex。建造自动防御系统，升级移动平台，在风暴和系统故障期间部署应对措施。守护脆弱的人类种子，确保庇护所即使遭受万军围攻也能屹立不倒。防护系统的战略选择，将决定最后一代人类的最终命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783560/extras/1b9b31d85b65bd26962e54bfca4b6631.poster.avif?t=1770805760\" width=780 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783560/extras/1b9b31d85b65bd26962e54bfca4b6631.webm?t=1770805760\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783560/extras/1b9b31d85b65bd26962e54bfca4b6631.mp4?t=1770805760\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >将火箭发射入轨</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >回收并重新激活旧世界的MOSES火箭发射基础设施，将重获新生的人类发射升空，帮他们逃离这颗正逐渐被海洋淹没的星球。搜寻发射密码，提炼火箭燃料，重建导航AI，确保任务成功进行。每次发射都伴随着精确计算过的风险，但为了物种的存续，这点风险值得一冒。目送你亲手培育出的人类升入轨道，让他们带走人类未来的希望。</p>",
